<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center; padding:4pt; line-height:1.25em; text-align:center; font-size:8pt;"><a href="/wiki/File:Shen_Kua.JPG" class="image" title="Shen Kuo, a Chinese scientist famous for his concepts of true north and land formation, among others.  (Modern artist's impression)"><img alt="Shen Kuo, a Chinese scientist famous for his concepts of true north and land formation, among others.  (Modern artist's impression)" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/40/Shen_Kua.JPG/225px-Shen_Kua.JPG" width="225" height="203" border="0" /></a><br />
<div style="padding-top:0.3em; line-height:1.2em;"><span style="">Shen Kuo, a Chinese scientist famous for his concepts of <a href="/wiki/True_north" title="True north">true north</a> and <a href="/wiki/Geomorphology" title="Geomorphology">land formation</a>, among others.<br /></span>
