<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Shen_Kuo&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<p><cite id="cnote_a"><a href="#ref_a" title=""><b>^</b></a></cite>&#160;<b>a:</b>&#160;See the article <a href="/wiki/Society_of_the_Song_Dynasty" title="Society of the Song Dynasty">Society of the Song Dynasty</a>.<br />
<cite id="cnote_b"><a href="#ref_b" title=""><b>^</b></a></cite>&#160;<b>b:</b>&#160;Refer to the <i>Partisans and factions, reformers and conservatives</i> section of the article <a href="/wiki/History_of_the_Song_Dynasty" title="History of the Song Dynasty">History of the Song Dynasty</a>.<br />
<cite id="cnote_c"><a href="#ref_c" title=""><b>^</b></a></cite>&#160;<b>c:</b>&#160;From his biography in the <i>Dictionary of Scientific Biography</i> (New York 1970–1990)<br />
<cite id="cnote_d"><a href="#ref_d" title=""><b>^</b></a></cite>&#160;<b>d:</b>&#160;For more, see <a href="/wiki/Architecture_of_the_Song_Dynasty" title="Architecture of the Song Dynasty">Architecture of the Song Dynasty</a>.<br />
